definition.text: WOW! I like what I see!

paragraphs.text: My first impression is just: WOW
Someone really wanted to develop something completely unique.
Impressive Tutorials: They must have been a ton of work.
Playfull User Interface: I can see the interest to bring gamification to trading

I am basically a visual person and therefore hope that the great visiualization of the bots trading actions will help me to develop working and profitable trading strategies. Because till now I am a more or less novice to trading and the crypto world.
